        "content": "<p>Xavier, I think your question about whether or not you \"use Tendsto.add\" is the same as asking \"should I prove that addition is continuous (e.g. by using epsilon/2 somewhere, which is the key input) or assume it?\" Of course, this is up to you :-)</p>",
